----------------------------------------------------------------
Reference materials
----------------------------------------------------------------

The PCB outline geometry used in this case design is derived from
official D-Robotics RDK X5 mechanical drawings (STEP and DXF files)
published at https://archive.d-robotics.cc/downloads/hardware/rdk_x5/ .
Those reference files remain the property of D-Robotics and are
included in the `reference/` directory for design verification only.
This case design itself (OpenSCAD source, STL outputs, documentation)
is the original work of the author and licensed under CC BY 4.0.
